reviewText: Excellent service and video! Received in a timely manner and in new condition like it said. I love Zac Efron, so I was excited to see there was a video about his life.  He's so CUTE!
Great informative video about Zac Efron. From his small beginnings to where he is now. This would be a wonderful video for any Zac fan.

This is an interesting little documentary that I stumbled upon by accident. Its only an hour long, and it doesn't really give you any information that you wouldn't already know (or want to know) about Zac. Worth a rent, but maybe not a buy.
